{"tid":25554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Easy Run： 高強度間歇訓練增耐力","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T11:32:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f52081aa9cf290dc78bc6bb091b326f1eb3536eb","tid":25554,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856427&d=l69NtrdJdk8sA6p%2BnNs83QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ae527da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856427&h=5730f5d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856427</a><br />\n<br />\nEasy Run：<br />\n高強度間歇訓練增耐力<br />\n<br />\n9,269<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n 【重複跑】<br />\n【重複跑】<br />\n高強度間歇訓練能有效提升心肺功能及改善肌肉力量，中大矯形外科及創傷學系講師李韋煜博士表示，此訓練可用於提升跑手或其他運動員，如足球、籃球運動員的心肺耐力表現。進行期間運動強度要達到最高心跳80%至95%，故初學者應該量力而為，先從每課4至8個重複次數為基礎，即約5至10分鐘的訓練，循序漸進地增加重複次數、組數和持續時間。<br />\n以跑步為例，可做2至8次重複跑，快跑及快走互相間斷。例如快跑10至20秒，然後快走1至2分鐘作小休。要提升運動強度及肌肉力量，可於休息時段加入徒手力量訓練的動作，例如俯卧撐，箭步蹲等。<br />\n■記者梁麗兒<br />\n<br />\n重複跑<br />\n快跑10至20秒，然後快走1至2分鐘為1次，可重複跑2至8次，宜循序漸進增加次數<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n掌上壓<br />\n快跑10至20秒，然後做掌上壓5至10次為1次，可重複做2至8次，宜循序漸進增加次數<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n箭步蹲<br />\n快跑10至20秒，然後做箭步蹲5至10下為1次，可重複做2至8次，宜循序漸進增加次數。箭步蹲即前後腳蹲下，左腳屈成90度，右腳向後下降。左右腳輪流做<br />\n<br />\n示範：中大香港賽馬會運動醫學及健康科學中心項目協調員黃曉淋<br />\n攝影：周智堅<br />\n<br />\n想輕輕鬆鬆健康啲，記住留意健康蘋台<br />\n<a href=\"http://health.appledaily.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.appledaily.com.hk%2F&d=l69NtrdJdk8sA6p%2BnNs83QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4ad02d46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://health.appledaily.com.hk/</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n全智賢最愛浸清酒浴無助瘦身　或令皮膚變乾發炎<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n運動隊醫隨想：與時並進的運動醫學發展"},{"pid":"7922d28f670b0fe6cadb67acfce50b7efb8f2588","tid":25554,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161206/org/1480965844_19b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161206%2Forg%2F1480965844_19b6.jpg&h=a44ef19b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4a1fae2cc5ccbc016798dec7f63ca182f0ac3ec","tid":25554,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"咁都當新聞  毒果記者on 撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n btw  thx for sharing 樓主"},{"pid":"c438048a585a0e487c6adb9292e2d8d2c8bdf79a","tid":25554,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都當新聞  毒果記者on 撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n btw  thx for sharing 樓主</blockquote><br />\n哩個時代騙徒手法層出不窮"},{"pid":"f66b17da2de8b0aa097fb3b0ebad7dd1cf835c27","tid":25554,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"easy run<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d真係會練到暈同嘔"},{"pid":"1ade39af88a63da3fdc4a9e7cb64303b9b30433f","tid":25554,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"hiit點easy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91c44ca5c5b2df0689429d9f482cb6cb2f6046e","tid":25554,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"爆10～20秒，休1分咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n唔係爆10、休20咋咩"},{"pid":"057c569872248189a5846d